OL,3,C'Heartbreaking': Animal sanctuary
OL,4,Cfaces uncertain future due to drop in
OL,5,Cfunding
OL,7,FVideo report by Hannah Norbury
OL,9,FAn animal rescue charity fears it may
OL,10,Fhave to close its doors for good due
OL,11,Fto soaring costs and a drop in funding.
OL,13,FAlbert's Horse Sanctuary in Barnsley,
OL,14,Fwhich has rescued horses, donkeys,
OL,15,Fgoats and even pigs, relies on
OL,16,Fdonations. But now the founders worry
OL,17,Fthe future of the animals could be at
OL,18,Frisk.
