OL,7,FThe charity says donations have been
OL,8,Fslowing down for some time, but the
OL,9,Fcosts of feeding the more than 50
OL,10,Fanimals and vet bills has stayed in
OL,11,Fthe thousands.
OL,13,FStacey Hepworth, a trustee at the
OL,14,Fsanctuary said: "It's been quite a
OL,15,Flong time now that we've worried about
OL,16,Fthe sanctuary's future but we've just
OL,17,Ftried to push on.
