OL,3,C'Heartbreaking': Animal sanctuary
OL,4,Cfaces uncertain future due to drop in
OL,5,Cfunding
OL,7,F"A lot of sanctuaries at the minute I
OL,8,Fthink are struggling really bad just
OL,9,Flike us, and it's impossible for them
OL,10,Fto take on more animals, so they would
OL,11,Fhave to be put to sleep most of them,
OL,12,Fthat's heartbreaking, they literally
OL,13,Fare our everything.
OL,15,F"I don't want to think about that."
OL,17,FTo try and help minimise the financial
OL,18,Fpressure, the charity set up a go fund
OL,19,Fme page with a target of #5,000, which
OL,20,Fwould help them for a while.
