OL,7,FSo far it has raised just over #1,100.
OL,9,FMary Hepworth, a founder of the
OL,10,Fsanctuary said: "The biggest thing is
OL,11,Fthe income continuously coming in, and
OL,12,Fthat's what is scary.
OL,14,F"It's no good people helping us now
OL,15,Ffor a month, and then what happens
OL,16,Fnext month? We've got to find a way of
OL,17,Fthat income continuously coming in."
